hcc_text: 79th Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Brooklyn)
info: At 79th Street at Gowanus Exwy Wb En Fort Hamilton P, Seventh Avenue and Fort Hamilton Parkway, there were 2 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
intersection: 79th Street at Gowanus Exwy Wb En Fort Hamilton P, Seventh Avenue and Fort Hamilton Parkway
